---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Garlic Butter Baby Broccoli with Capsicum & Mayonnaise
description: You think you know crumbed chicken? Think again! With a creamy mayo in the mix, it goes from tasty to totally
irresistible. Paired with an assortment of veggies for extra deliciousness, you'll be talking about this long after
you've scooped up the final crumbs.

